I believe all the parts come from the same place. Passenger side with
battery clamp from VW, driver's side w/o from Klokkerholm. At least my parts
were.

I think BD has the dates wrong. The tail changed in 72 for the larger
taillights and it should probably read 72-79. ETKA bears this out.

